		<title>有成精密WINAICO發表全新一代｢背接觸式｣太陽能模組WBC極致黑曜系列</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/01/%e6%9c%89%e6%88%90%e7%b2%be%e5%af%86winaico%e7%99%bc%e8%a1%a8%e5%85%a8%e6%96%b0%e4%b8%80%e4%bb%a3%ef%bd%a2%e8%83%8c%e6%8e%a5%e8%a7%b8%e5%bc%8f%ef%bd%a3%e5%a4%aa%e9%99%bd%e8%83%bd%e6%a8%a1%e7%b5%84wbc/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 01 Sep 2025 06:23:56 +0000</pubDate>
